flowchart TD
    Start([Start Linear Search]) --> GetTarget[Get Target ID/Name from User]
    GetTarget --> InitVars[Initialize:<br/>comparisons = 0<br/>index = 0]
    InitVars --> CheckList{index < list.size}

    CheckList -->|Yes| IncrementComp[comparisons++]
    IncrementComp --> GetEmployee[employee = list.get index]
    GetEmployee --> Compare{Match Found?<br/>employee.id == target OR<br/>employee.name.contains target}

    Compare -->|Yes| Found[Found Employee!]
    Found --> DisplayComp1[Display: Completed in X comparisons]
    DisplayComp1 --> DisplayResult[Display Employee Details]
    DisplayResult --> ReturnEmployee[Return employee]
    ReturnEmployee --> End([End Search])

    Compare -->|No| IncrementIndex[index++]
    IncrementIndex --> CheckList

    CheckList -->|No| NotFound[Employee Not Found]
    NotFound --> DisplayComp2[Display: Completed in X comparisons<br/>Not found]
    DisplayComp2 --> ReturnNull[Return null]
    ReturnNull --> End

    style Start fill:#90EE90
    style End fill:#FFB6C1
    style Found fill:#98FB98
    style NotFound fill:#FF6B6B
    style Compare fill:#FFD700
    style CheckList fill:#87CEEB
    style DisplayResult fill:#DDA0DD

    note1[Time Complexity: O n]
    note2[Space Complexity: O 1]
    note3[Best Case: O 1 - found at first position]
    note4[Worst Case: O n - found at last position or not found]
    note5[Use: Small datasets, partial matching, unsorted data]

